sinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/e0ccd96cac30e04499bbee435a7cc33e.poster.avif?t=1716363744\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/e0ccd96cac30e04499bbee435a7cc33e.webm?t=1716363744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/e0ccd96cac30e04499bbee435a7cc33e.mp4?t=1716363744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/60e0cabbf235669883d2f6dc60915cfa.webp?t=1716363744\" width=620 height=56 /></span><br><br>・You are a little tired today, let's shoot a can to make you feel better. For those nights...<br>・Translation may be lousy. However, you should be able to clear it with feeling, so we hope you will forgive us...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/0907f96e95d93086ee4fac0339cafdc6.gif?t=1716363744\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/0907f96e95d93086ee4fac0339cafdc6.poster.avif?t=1716363744\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2925270/extras/ee9ae5190a283175734a5af24d2c4e4d.avif?t=1716363744\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br>(teaser movie BGM By MusMus)",
